<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Sign-in Link</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #222; line-height: 1.5;">
  <h2 style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Hello {{fullName}},</h2>
  <p style="margin-top: 0;">Use the button below to sign in. The link expires in {{expiresInMinutes}} minutes.</p>
  <p style="margin: 16px 0;">
    <a href="{{frontendBaseUrl}}/auth/magic?token={{token}}" style="background:#2563eb;color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;">
      Sign in
    </a>
  </p>
  <p>If the button does not work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
  <p style="word-break: break-all;">{{frontendBaseUrl}}/auth/magic?token={{token}}</p>
  <p style="margin-top:24px;">Thank you,<br/>LRC Jeunesse</p>
</body>
</html>
